    <item>
      <title>Art</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/art/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/art/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 class=&#34;text-lg font-medium mb-4&#34;&gt;Art &amp; Effort&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I think I’ve always had a knack for doing math or philosophy. This is much less true for art, where I’ve had to work very hard to get from drawing like &lt;a href=&#34;#&#34; onclick=&#34;openImageModal(); return false;&#34;&gt;this&lt;/a&gt; in my early 30s to being able to create what you can see &lt;a href=&#34;https://krita-artists.org/u/nicogreu/activity/portfolio&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&#xA; or &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.instagram.com/duduqdrawstuff/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This reflects how I work. I always put a lot of effort in what I do. And I always make sure the things I produce are visually and artistically compelling.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Collaboration</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/collaboration/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/collaboration/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;My scientific background makes me particularly interested in &lt;strong&gt;collaborating&lt;/strong&gt; with other philosophers on &lt;strong&gt;experimental philosophy projects&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I have assisted many social science students and researchers in refining experimental designs similar to those typically used in experimental philosophy. Combined with my strong research methods expertise, this experience has given me a particularly &lt;strong&gt;sharp eye for good designs&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you are planning an experimental philosophy project, I would love to be involved.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Consulting</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/consulting/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/consulting/</guid>
      <description>&lt;!-- &#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;text-lg font-medium mb-4&#34;&gt;Research Consulting to Nonprofits&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;As a consultant, I provide nonprofit and mission-driven organizations with high-level support across the full research lifecycle.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;h3 class=&#34;text-lg font-medium mb-4&#34;&gt;Consulting style: Short &amp; Intense&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;Rather than long-term, open-ended contracts, I specialize in short, intensive consulting sprints. For a short period of time (typically a few days to a couple of weeks), I work as an extension of your team to help resolve a specific research-related challenge.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&#xA; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;h3 class=&#34;text-lg font-medium mb-4&#34;&gt;Sprint Menu&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;Here is a non-exhaustive list of services I can offer, with very rough price range and turnaround:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;overflow-x-auto&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;table class=&#34;min-w-full bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;th class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left&#34;&gt;Service&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;        &lt;th class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left&#34;&gt;Deliverable&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;        &lt;th class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left&#34;&gt;Turnaround&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;        &lt;th class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left&#34;&gt;Indicative Price Range&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;    &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Research design sprint&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Study design plan (3-5 pages) + 1-hour consultation to align on methodology, sample size, and ethical considerations&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;3-5 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;2000-3500€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Power &amp; Feasibility Analysis&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;2-4 page power analysis report with required sample size, feasibility assessment, and recommendations&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;2-3 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;1200-2500€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Research Methodology Audit&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;2-4 page methodology evaluation with strengths, weaknesses, risks, and actionable fixes&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;3-5 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;1500-3000€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Rapid Data/Statistical Analysis&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;3-5 page analysis report with cleaned data, statistical insights, and visualizations (2-3 charts/graphs)&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;4-7 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;2500-4000€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Rapid evidence review&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;5-12 page synthesis of existing research, key gaps, and actionable recommendations&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;5-7 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;2000-4000€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Policy Briefs&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;2-4 page policy brief with executive summary, context, evidence, recommendations, and 1-2 visuals&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;3-5 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;1700-3200€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Grant Application Support&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;1-3 page methodology section + power analysis&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;4-7 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;1800-3500€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Light Impact Evaluation Framework&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;6-12 page design of a lightweight but complete evaluation framework (indicators, data sources, analysis plan)&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;7-12 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;3000-5000€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;!-- &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Light Interactive data tool&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Basic monitoring or visualization dashboard (e.g., R Shiny), with a 1-page user guide&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;7-12 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;4000-6000€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt; --&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;overflow-x-auto&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h3 class=&#34;text-lg font-medium mb-4&#34;&gt;Add-ons&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;  &lt;table class=&#34;min-w-full bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;th class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left&#34;&gt;Service&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;        &lt;th class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left&#34;&gt;Deliverable&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;        &lt;th class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left&#34;&gt;Turnaround&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;        &lt;th class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left&#34;&gt;Indicative Price Range&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;    &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Visual data communication&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;A custom infographics summary of reports or findings&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;+1-2 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;+500-1000€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr class=&#34;hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;Comic-based communication&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;1 or several comic pages synthesizing a report or explaining research in an engaging and non-technical way&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700&#34;&gt;+2-7 days&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;        &lt;td class=&#34;py-2 px-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 whitespace-nowrap&#34;&gt;+500-3000€&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;And here are a few pages extracted from my comic &lt;a href=&#34;https://crish.fr/en&#34; class=&#34;underline&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;font-crish italic text-lg&#34;&gt;crish&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, to give you an idea of what a few pages of comic-based communication could look like, without color (pages 1 to 4) and with color (pages 5 to 8):&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
