    <item>
      <title>Outreach</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/outreach/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/outreach/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 class=&#34;text-lg font-medium mb-4&#34;&gt;The Project &lt;span class=&#34;font-crish italic text-xl&#34;&gt;crish&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I have a dream that one day a blockbuster movie will invest a large portion of its budget in truly thoughtful educational content.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Until that happens, my comic &lt;a href=&#34;https://crish.fr/en&#34; class=&#34;underline&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;font-crish italic text-lg&#34;&gt;crish&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;mdash; a semi-fantastic story filled with absurd humor and brief &lt;strong&gt;insights about statistics and the research world&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;mdash; is my humble attempt to show that entertaining stories can also convey deep philosophical and educational ideas.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Research</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/research/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/research/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 class=&#34;text-lg font-medium mb-4&#34;&gt;Research in Analytic Philosophy&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;In philosophy, I am primarily interested in &lt;strong&gt;understanding how we can learn from data&lt;/strong&gt;, and in exploring whether &lt;em&gt;informal statistical reasoning&lt;/em&gt; can shed light on key questions in epistemology, decision theory and the philosophy of science.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;My secondary research interests include contributions to the niche branch of the &lt;strong&gt;philosophy of comics&lt;/strong&gt; and to the interdisciplinary field of &lt;strong&gt;experimental philosophy&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The research outputs resulting from my ongoing transition into these philosophical investigations are presented below.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
